'''İsmail Yüksek''' (born 26 January 1999) is a Turkish professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[Süper Lig]] side [[Fenerbahçe S.K. (football)|Fenerbahçe]] and the [[Turkey national football team|Turkey national team]].

==Club career==
===Youth and Gölcükspor===
Yüksek began his youth career with hometown club [[Bursaspor]] and also played in youth level with Bursa Merinosspor, [[Yeşil Bursa]], Yıldırım Belediyespor and Bursa Yıldırımspor. He started his professional career with [[Gölcükspor]] and played two successful season with them.

===Fenerbahçe===
Yüksek signed a five-year contract with [[Fenerbahçe S.K. (football)|Fenerbahçe]] on 2 May 2020.

====Loans====
On 5 October 2020, Yüksek joined [[Balıkesirspor]] on loan.

He returned to Fenerbahçe on 12 January 2021.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.hurriyet.com.tr/sporarena/ismail-yuksek-fenerbahceye-geri-dondu-ve-antrenmana-cikti-41713973|title=İsmail Yüksek, Fenerbahçe'ye geri döndü ve antrenmana çıktı|website=www.hurriyet.com.tr}}</ref> Yüksek made his professional debut with Fenerbahçe in a 3–1 [[Süper Lig]] win over [[MKE Ankaragücü]] on 18 January 2021.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://uk.soccerway.com/matches/2021/01/18/turkey/super-lig/fenerbahce-spor-kulubu/mke-ankaragucu/3352939/|title=Fenerbahçe vs. Ankaragücü - 18th January 2021 - Soccerway|website=uk.soccerway.com}}</ref>

On 1 February 2021, he joined [[Adana Demirspor]] on loan in the [[TFF First League]] for the second half of the 2020–21 season.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.fanatik.com.tr/adana-demirsporun-fenerbahceden-kiraladigi-ismail-yuksekin-hedefi-sampiyonluk-2199776|title=Adana Demirspor’un Fenerbahçe’den kiraladığı İsmail Yüksek’in...|website=Fanatik}}</ref>

He went on loan to [[Bursaspor]] for the 2021–22 season.<ref name="Fanatik 2022">{{cite web | title=İsmail Yüksek: Bursaspor hak ettiği yerlere ulaşacaktır | website=Fanatik | date=24 May 2022 | url=https://www.fanatik.com.tr/ismail-yuksek-bursaspor-hak-ettigi-yerlere-ulasacaktir-2284251 | language=tr | access-date=20 July 2022}}</ref>

====2022–23 season====
After return to Fenerbahçe, Yüksek made a very strong start to the 2022–23 season with coach [[Jorge Jesus]], made good use of his first 11 chances and called to the [[Turkey national football team|national team]].<ref>[https://www.fanatik.com.tr/ismail-yuksekin-muthis-yukselisi-once-fenerbahce-simdi-milli-takim-2302104 Flash start with Ismail Yüksek]</ref><ref>[https://www.trthaber.com/haber/spor/fenerbahceli-ismail-yuksek-performansiyla-dikkat-cekiyor-710229.html Fenerbahçeli İsmail Yüksek performansıyla dikkat çekiyor]</ref> On 6 October, he was selected [[man of the match]] by supporters votes for his performance in the [[2022–23 UEFA Europa League group stage|2022–23 UEFA Europa League Group B]] third week [[AEK Larnaca FC|AEK Larnaca]] match.<ref>[https://twitter.com/Fenerbahce/status/1578327754814083072 Fenerbahçe SK Official Twitter Account]</ref>

On 20 January 2023, Fenerbahçe announced to sign new contract with him until May 2027.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://fenerbahce.org/haberler/futbol/2023/1/ismail-yuksek-in-sozlesmesi-uzatildi|title=İsmail Yüksek’in sözleşmesi uzatıldı|website=Fenerbahce.org|date=20 January 2023}}</ref>

====2023–24 season====
In his second season as a starter in the team, he made his top performance with new coach and team's local legend [[İsmail Kartal]], he consolidate his place with Fenerbahçe and international team.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.odatv4.com/spor/ismail-yuksekten-goz-alan-performans-65-binden-4-milyona-86706363|title=İsmail Yüksek'ten göz alan performans: 65 binden 4 milyona|website=Oda TV}}</ref> He changed his shirt number from 80 to 5.<ref>[https://x.com/TekYolFener/status/1694360853540212791?s=20 İsmail Yüksek'in yeni forma numarası 5 oldu]</ref>

====2024–25 season====
On 20 December 2024, he made his 100th appearances in all competitions for Fenerbahçe against [[Eyüpspor]] in a 1-1 [[Süper Lig]] away tie.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fenerbahce.org/haberler/futbol/2024/12/ikas-eyupspor-1-1-fenerbahce |title=ikas Eyüpspor 1-1 Fenerbahçe |date=20 December 2025 |accessdate=14 April 2025 |website=fenerbahce.org|language=tr}}</ref>

On 28 March 2025, he extended his contract with Fenerbahçe until May 2028.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.trtspor.com.tr/haber/futbol/fenerbahce-ismail-yuksekin-sozlesmesini-uzatti-26019884|title=Fenerbahçe İsmail Yüksek'in sözleşmesini uzattı
|website=TRTspor|date=15 May 2025}}</ref>

====2025–26 season====
On 2 November 2025, he scored his first league goal for Fenerbahçe against [[Beşiktaş J.K.|Beşiktaş]] in a 2-3 [[Süper Lig]] away [[Beşiktaş–Fenerbahçe rivalry (football)|derby]] victory.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://fenerbahce.org/haberler/futbol/2025/11/besiktas-2-3-fenerbahce |title=Beşiktaş 2-3 Fenerbahçe |publisher=Fenerbahçe S.K. |language=tr |date=2 November 2025 }}</ref>

==International career==
Without any youth international experience, Yüksek made his international debut against [[Luxembourg national football team|Luxembourg]] on 22 September 2022, coming on as an 81st minute substitute and he scored his first goal six minutes later. He wasn't selected to the Turkey youth national teams and directly played for senior level.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.tff.org/Default.aspx?pageId=30&kisiId=1427164  |title=Player profile @ TFF.org |publisher=TFF.org |access-date=15 October 2023}}</ref>

On 12 October 2023, he has become the first player to record 15+ duels and 10+ possessions won in a single [[UEFA Euro 2024 qualifying Group D|Euro 2024 qualifier]] game, winning 16 duels and recovering 12 possessions against [[Croatia national football team|Croatia]].<ref>[https://x.com/OptaCan/status/1712571612556316790?s=20 OptaCan statistics]</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.cumhuriyet.com.tr/spor/istatistikleri-altust-etti-ismail-yuksekten-hirvatistan-karsisinda-2-2129619  |title=İstatistikleri altüst etti: İsmail Yüksek'ten Hırvatistan karşısında 2 rekor |publisher=cumhuriyet.com |access-date=13 October 2023}}</ref>

==Style of play==
Yüksek is a talented, tenacious, and physically strong, all-round box-to-box midfielder, who is capable of defending well, due to his vision, technique, aggressive tackling, athletic attributes, stamina, and his powerful and accurate shot from distance with his right foot. A versatile, powerful, and hard-working player, he is capable of playing center  and defensive midfield position, and adapting himself to several different formations, but usually operated in the centre of the pitch.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.transfermerkez.com/2020/02/scout-raporu-ismail-yuksek.html  |title=Scout Raporu: İsmail Yüksek |publisher=transfermerkez.com |date=26 February 2020}}</ref>

